# 🎮 EmuHub – Android Emulation Central

[![Website](https://img.shields.io/badge/🌐-Live_Demo-4f8ef7)](https://your-actual-demo-link.com)
[![GitHub release](https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/YOUR_USERNAME/emuhub)](https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/emuhub/releases)

**One place for GPU drivers, Winlator mods, game patches, and every tool you need to run PC games on Android.**

EmuHub is a community-friendly static web app that centralises the best resources for Android PC emulation.

---

## ✨ Features

* 🔥 Auto-updated A8xx driver (Turnip Gen8)
* 🎮 Turnip GPU drivers (Adreno 6xx / 7xx / Zink)
* 🪟 Winlator builds (Official, Cmod, Ludashi)
* 🛠 Tools: GameHub, DXVK, VKD3D, Box64, FexCore
* 📱 Fully responsive layout
* ⚡ Quick-start guide

---

## 🖼 Screenshot

![EmuHub Screenshot](https://via.placeholder.com/800x400)

---

## 🚀 How to use

1. Open `index.html` in your browser
2. Latest driver loads automatically
3. Click **Download** buttons
4. Follow setup guide

